item.title: About
item.description: This webpage is made by: Ellen Winther Mortensen, Julius Pulvertaft Rasmussen, and Michelle Siw Hovendal and is part of the final project in the course Social Data Analysis and Vissualization at Technical University of Denmark (DTU). This webpage is made in the spring 2021. The aim of the webpage is about restaurants placed in North America, the data is based on yelp data. The Python explainer notebook is attached here.
